  <ul><li>1. Slot 4 (composite 5.00/5) - Usable as-is: The variant asks the same selection‑sort intermediate‑state question with new numbers, maintains difficulty and clarity, and has a single correct answer.</li><li>2. Slot 6 (composite 5.00/5) - Usable as-is: The variant preserves the same multi‑level indexing and method‑call reasoning with clear wording and a single correct answer.</li><li>3. Slot 7 (composite 5.00/5) - Usable as-is: The variant mirrors the original nested-loop condition‑checking task with a new locker context, keeping difficulty, clarity, and answer structure intact.</li></ul>
  <h3>Low-rated variant (1 example)</h3>
  <ul><li>Slot 38 (composite 2.00/5) - Usable as-is: The variant asks the same reliability concept with identical options, same difficulty and clear answer, differing only by minor rewording.</li></ul>

